The '''Burkinabé Swimming and Life Saving Federation''' ({{lang-fr|Federation Burkinabe de Natation et de Sauvetage}}), is the national governing body for the sport of [[swimming (sport)|swimming]] in [[Burkina Faso]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Federation Burkinabe de Natation et de Sauvetage|url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=444:bot-botswana&catid=91:africa&Itemid=638|publisher=[[FINA]]|accessdate=3 August 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120816141314/http://www.fina.org/H2O/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=444:bot-botswana&catid=91:africa&Itemid=638#|archive-date=2012-08-16|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref>

