'''Czech Republic women's national inline hockey team''' is the national team for [[Czech Republic]]. The team finished fifth at the [[2011 Women's World Inline Hockey Championships]].<ref name=2011champs>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldinlinehockey.org/2011/07/ranking-2011-world-inline-hockey-championships/ |title=Ranking 2011 World Inline Hockey Championships |publisher=World Inline Hockey |date=9 July 2011 |accessdate=7 February 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221133547/http://www.worldinlinehockey.org/2011/07/ranking-2011-world-inline-hockey-championships/ |archivedate=21 February 2014 |df= }}</ref>

