'''KK Pelister''' ({{lang-mk|КК Пелистер}}) is a [[basketball]] club based in [[Bitola]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. They currently play in the [[Macedonian First League (basketball)|Macedonian First League]].

==History==
The club was founded in 1948.


Name: Mladost Metalec (92-96), Pelister (96-06), Swisslion Pelister (06-09), Pelister (09-11), Pelister Sport (11-14), Pelister (14-15), KK Pelister AD Bitola (2015)

==Honours==

'''Macedonian Republic League'''
* Winners (3): 1974, 1989, 1991

===[[Macedonian First League (basketball)|Macedonian League]]===
* Semifinalist - 2006, 2007, 2009
* Macedonian D2 Runner-Up - 2012

===[[Macedonian Basketball Cup|Macedonian Cup]]===
* Macedonian Cup Finalist - 2009
* Macedonian Cup Semifinalist - 2008

