{{Infobox cricket ground | ground_name = Lune Road Ground | nickname = | country = England | image = Lancaster Cricket Club - geograph.org.uk - 35896.jpg | location = [[Lancaster, Lancashire|Lancaster]], [[Lancashire]] | establishment = 1907 <small>(first recorded match)</small> | seating_capacity = | end1 = | end2 = | year1 = 1914 | club1 = [[Lancashire County Cricket Club|Lancashire]] | date = 4 September | year = 2010 | source = https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/565.html profile }}
'''Lune Road Ground''' is a [[cricket]] ground in [[Lancaster, Lancashire|Lancaster]], [[Lancashire]]. The ground is situated on the bank of the [[River Lune]]. The first recorded match on the ground was in 1907, when the [[Lancashire County Cricket Club|Lancashire Second XI]] played [[Durham County Cricket Club|Durham]] in the [[Minor Counties Championship]].<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/565_minc.html Minor Counties Championship Matches played on Lune Road Ground]</ref>
In 1914, the ground held its only [[first-class cricket|first-class]] match when [[Lancashire County Cricket Club|Lancashire]] played [[Warwickshire County Cricket Club|Warwickshire]] in the [[1914 County Championship|County Championship]].<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/565_f.html First-Class Matches played on Lune Road Ground]</ref>
With the first recorded match on the ground in 1907 involving the Lancashire Second XI, the ground has since held a combined total of 9 Second XI fixtures for the Lancashire Second XI in the Minor Counties Championship, [[Second XI Championship]] and Second XI Trophy up to 1995.<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/565_sec.html Second XI Championship Matches played on Lune Road Ground]</ref><ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/565_set.html Second XI Trophy Matches played on Lune Road Ground]</ref>
In local domestic cricket, the ground is the home venue of [[Lancaster Cricket Club]]<ref>[http://lancaster.play-cricket.com/home/home.asp Lancaster Cricket Club] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120713203435/http://lancaster.play-cricket.com/home/home.asp |date=2012-07-13 }}</ref> who play in the [[Northern Premier Cricket League]].
